        <mxCell id="matrix" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F8FAFC;strokeColor=#64748B;align=left;spacingLeft=14;fontSize=13" value="Plane-1：历史已完成；V3.0-PhaseA~E 回归保护；V3.x+ Web/Video UI 前置&lt;br&gt;Plane-2：PhaseA scope params、PhaseB/C RPC 合同已收官；PhaseD/E 受 facade / validation 影响；V3.x+ SDK/低代码协议&lt;br&gt;Plane-3：PhaseA ScopeContext、PhaseC Job/Artifact/Governance 已收官；PhaseD/E 验证 reference pack 复用能力；V3.x+ Memory/Feedback&lt;br&gt;Plane-4：PhaseC RuntimeAdapter governance 已收官；PhaseD/E 执行链路验证；V3.x+ 多 runtime 扩展&lt;br&gt;Plane-5：PhaseB PackAssemblyResult 已收官；PhaseD Meeting reference pack；PhaseE Knowledge reference pack；V3.x+ Interview/Investment/Video/Low-Code&lt;br&gt;Plane-6：PhaseA scope migration、PhaseB connector security、PhaseC artifact/job policy 已收官；PhaseD/E MCP connectors；V3.x+ 外部 store/GPU/视频工具" vertex="1">
