        <mxCell id="plan_text" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF7ED;strokeColor=#EA580C;align=left;spacingLeft=12;fontSize=13;arcSize=5;" value="PhaseA 专项文件：&lt;br&gt;docs/design/V3.0/v3_phasea_multi_app_core_readiness.md&lt;br&gt;docs/design/V3.0/v3_phasea_multi_app_core_readiness_acceptance.md&lt;br&gt;PhaseB 专项文件：&lt;br&gt;docs/design/V3.0/v3_phaseb_pack_connector_registry.md&lt;br&gt;本图与 current-vs-target-gap_v3.md、CURRENT-STATUS_v3.md 同步维护。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseA：Multi-App Core Readiness&lt;br&gt;状态：COMPLETED / FROZEN BASELINE（2026-05-06）&lt;br&gt;目标：冻结 AppProfile -&gt; ScopeContext -&gt; Gateway/Core service -&gt; Store 主链路&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseB：Pack 装配与 Connector 注册表&lt;br&gt;状态：COMPLETED / PHASE CLOSEOUT BASELINE（2026-05-08）&lt;br&gt;当前事实：PackAssemblyResult、connector descriptor/security、AppProfile pack_paths、registry-derived assembly、external pack target_version policy 已收官&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseC：Job / Artifact / Governance Hardening&lt;br&gt;状态：COMPLETED / PHASE CLOSEOUT BASELINE（2026-05-08）&lt;br&gt;当前事实：job 状态机、failure_context、connector approval retry、job/connector scope 隔离、ARTIFACT_READ_BLOCKED、artifact lineage、RuntimeAdapter governance injection 已收官；默认全量回归 182 passed / 3 skipped&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseD：Meeting reference pack validation&lt;br&gt;状态：VALIDATION PASSED&lt;br&gt;D0 文档同步；D1 Pack Assembly；D2 Connector Contracts；D3 Standard Workflow；D4 Legacy Facade；D5 Equivalence / Lineage；D6 Strict + Resilience E2E；D7 Architecture / Acceptance Docs&lt;br&gt;当前事实：Meeting Pack assembly、legacy facade equivalence、strict/resilience real-audio E2E 已通过；业务分析质量继续由外部 Meeting MCP 迭代&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseE：Knowledge reference pack validation&lt;br&gt;状态：REAL DATA SERVICE MCP E2E PASSED&lt;br&gt;当前事实：source_reference / note / brief / citation_bundle 四件套、data_service_mcp semantic capabilities、data boundary、lineage/job/trace binding、connector replacement fixture 已落地；focused regression 32 passed；迁移后的 /workspace/data_service 真实 MCP E2E status=passed" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="740" width="900" x="60" y="1450" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="accept_header" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ECFDF5;strokeColor=#059669;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1" value="V3.0 验收里程碑" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="900" x="1040" y="1380" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="accept_text" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ECFDF5;strokeColor=#059669;align=left;spacingLeft=12;fontSize=13;arcSize=3;" value="V3.0-PhaseA：AC01 profiles；AC02 scope 隔离；AC03 legacy 回填；AC04 RPC scope；AC05 meeting 回归&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseB：AC01 Pack manifest；AC02 PackAssemblyResult；AC03 external pack paths；AC04 Connector Registry；AC05 connector security；AC06 sample-pack neutrality；AC07 descriptor-driven assembly&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseC：AC01 job 状态 queued/running/completed/failed/cancelled；AC02 artifact read policy；AC03 lineage；AC04 治理覆盖；AC05 RuntimeAdapter injection；AC06 platform-neutral governance&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseD：AC00 preconditions；AC01 pack assembly；AC02 connector contracts；AC03 standard workflow；AC04 legacy facade warning；AC05 equivalence / lineage；AC06 strict + resilience E2E；AC07 无新增平台业务旁路&lt;br&gt;V3.0-PhaseE：AC01 Knowledge MCP E2E；AC02 data boundary；AC03 connector replacement；AC04 source_reference / note / brief / citation_bundle artifacts；AC05 lineage/job/trace 完整性&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PhaseC 收官证据（2026-05-08）：默认全量回归 182 passed / 3 skipped / 6 warnings；PhaseC + Meeting 切片 14 passed / 1 skipped&lt;br&gt;PhaseD 收官证据（2026-05-08）：full regression 193 passed / 3 skipped / 6 warnings；focused regression 23 passed / 1 skipped；preflight status=ok；resilience E2E status=passed strict=false；strict E2E status=passed strict=true；产出 transcript / analysis / result / minutes + connector_result 证据节点&lt;br&gt;PhaseE 证据（2026-05-09）：focused regression 32 passed；真实 MCP E2E status=passed；artifact kinds=source_reference/note/brief/citation_bundle；lineage_count=4；trace_count=27&lt;br&gt;默认入口：tests/；scripts/e2e_meeting_validation.sh；scripts/e2e_knowledge_validation.sh；根目录历史 test_*.py 不作为默认入口" vertex="1">
